salutations my friend!

As a reminder, we have another meeting next general meeting next week in Wheeler 123, Wednesday March 7th at 6:00pm. SAME BAT TIME, SAME BAT PLACE!!!

Our next issue is coming out the following week, so please look out for us on Upper Sproul. Just say hi or something . . . we get lonely ;___;

In the meantime, while we frantically try to get this issue to the printers, [please enjoy these progressive, feminist, API, [add your own adjective here] comics here by the very talented Wendy Xu. ](http://angrygirlcomics.tumblr.com/)

*End Transmission*

